entries.journal_entry_description: Lady Valarian is not done with Jabba. She plans to punish him more and is asking for your help.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Destroy the Hutt smuggler that is trying to get out of the system.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Once you have succeeded in destroying the Hutt smuggler return to Lady Valarian.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Jabba is sending a hit squad to kill Lady Valarian. She wants to publicly humiliate Jabba and have you destroy the assassination squad out in the streets so that Jabba will know that she won't stand for his strong arm tactics.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Jabba is sending an assassination squad to kill Valarian. The lady wants you to stop them in a nice public place, so that Jabba will know that she won't stand for his strong arm tactics She want to publicly humilate Jabba and have you destory the assassination squad out in the streets
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Your ambush of the assassination squad went off perfectly. Return to Lady Valarian with the good news.
